        <mxCell id="train-detail" value="1. prepare_data.py&#xa;   Burton ODE on CSV → enriched dataset&#xa;   Compute residual = dst − dst_burton&#xa;&#xa;2. train_anomaly.py  → Agent 2&#xa;   LSTM Autoencoder on quiet windows&#xa;&#xa;3. train_corrector.py → Agent 3&#xa;   LSTM on residual target&#xa;&#xa;4. pretrain_arbiter.py → Agent 4&#xa;   Behavioral cloning warm-start"
